deejayd (0.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * 0.4 Release.
  * Changes since 0.2
    * Add dvd support
    * Add a python library client
    * Add a command line client : djc
    * Improve performance and memory usage with the use of celementtree module
    * A lot of cleanups and bugfixes

